27
00:01:41,583 --> 00:01:47,573
This condition is independent of the
value of R0 and of U0.

28
00:01:47,573 --> 00:01:51,253
It should be noted that such a principle
can be used as continuous current.

29
00:01:51,253 --> 00:01:53,417
This is what we are going to work on today,

30
00:01:53,417 --> 00:01:56,228
